Pre-Game Insights: The Guyana Golden Jaguars are preparing for their crucial clash against Suriname in the Concacaf Nations League, with a press conference held to share thoughts on the game.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Tickets for the match are priced at G$2,000 and are available at the GFF office and the venue. Fans are encouraged to wear yellow in support of the team.
Others: The match is scheduled for September 5, 2024, at 4:00 pm at the National Track & Field Centre, Leonora.
